#Install and set up SASS

Download node. For windows OS, download and install the node LTS executable. IF you are using
linux, use copy and paste this command in your terminal:
"$ curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash"

After you have successfully installed node, proceed on install SASS by typing the following
command in your command prompt (for Windows OS) or terminal (for Linux OS):

"npm install sass -v 3.7.4"
